All the source files are under "src" directory.

This is a working prototype of a simple To-Do list application, in which one can perform following actions:

1. Create a new To-Do
2. Mark a To-Do as Done

Future Enhancements:

1. Add due-date aspect
2. Sort by due-date
3. Modify an existing To-Do
4. Delete a To-Do
5. Add user specific To-Dos (Login based)